obviously sit there and make

00:04:13.770 --> 00:04:16.250
the trade off of, well, if I
go for this, it's one code

00:04:16.250 --> 00:04:17.890
base, it's going to run
on all these devices.

00:04:17.890 --> 00:04:19.910
