what you need to do.

00:07:13.050 --> 00:07:15.320
And then when you start saying,
well, I'd really like

00:07:15.320 --> 00:07:17.570
it if it could just do this,
that's the point that they'll

00:07:17.570 --> 00:07:19.890
kind of say, look at the docs
and you'll find what you need.

00:07:19.890 --> 00:07:20.830
KRISPY UCCELLO: Awesome.

00:07:20.830 --> 00:07:26.580
So with the talk about voice
search and how excited

00:07:26.580 --> 00:07:29.090
