00:11:23.640 --> 00:11:28.530
fixed widths, fixed paddings,
moving it all into styles in

00:11:28.530 --> 00:11:30.760
the values kind of directory,
and generally getting to a

00:11:30.760 --> 00:11:33.190
point where everything was
shared and syncing up

00:11:33.190 --> 00:11:34.090
with the same page.

00:11:34.090 --> 00:11:36.630
At that point, it was nice and
easy just to start making

00:11:36.630 --> 00:11:38.980
little tweaks on different
versions whether it be on TV

00:11:38.980 --> 00:11:41.130
or tablet or phone.

00:11:41.130 --> 00:11:42.980
And yeah, just bringing
everything into one more

00:11:42.980 --> 00:11:47.030
