really focused on encouraging

00:11:53.990 --> 00:11:57.970
developers to have a very
similar look and feel while

00:11:57.970 --> 00:12:00.100
still bringing in their own
branding, their own elements

00:12:00.100 --> 00:12:03.430
of differentiation, but still
not expecting a user to learn

00:12:03.430 --> 00:12:05.470
an entirely new interface.

00:12:05.470 --> 00:12:07.460
So I think we found
a good balance.

